review_text: This Cressida in Pakistan is one of the cleanest models available. It features a complete maroon interior, immaculate engine bay, and impressive performance enhancements. With a 2JZ-GE engine, 6 puck clutch, W58 gearbox, Tein coilovers, and LSD differential, it offers a thrilling driving experience. The overall cleanliness, meticulousness, and satisfactory fuel economy on long routes make it highly desirable. A gem for those seeking a clean, powerful, and enjoyable ride.
